CatDescriptText: Cutline of article published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 25, 1960, pg. A11 reads: "4. The Pittsburgh Tire Co. booth was "loaded" with auto accessories, shown by representatives Ross Scott and R.O. Findley."
